        ": قُلْتُ لَهُ مَا اَلْمُحْصَنُ رَحِمَكَ اَللَّهُ قَالَ \"مَنْ كَانَ لَهُ فَرْجٌ يَغْدُو عَلَيْهِ وَ يَرُوحُ فَهُوَ مُحْصَنٌ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.5022 - Abdullah ibn Sinan narrated from Ismail ibn Jabir, who reports by Abu Abdullah (as).\nI asked Imam (as): \"May Allah (swt) have mercy on you, who is considered Muhsan?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"Whoever has lawful access to a spouse in the morning and evening, he is Muhsan.\""
        ]
      }
